Istanbul Industrialists Confident for 2011, Hurriyet Reports

-- B y   S t e v e   B r y a n t
-- 
2011-02-18T05:59:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-18/istanbul-industrialists-confident-for-2011-hurriyet-reports.html
Industrialists in Istanbul,  Turkey ’s
biggest city, are more optimistic for the first half of this
year than they were in the last six months of 2010, Hurriyet
newspaper said.  The Istanbul Chamber of Industry’s index of expectations
advanced to 155 for the first half of 2011 from 136 six months
earlier, Hurriyet said, citing a survey of the chamber’s
members. The index ranges from zero to 200.  The companies surveyed are optimistic about the strength of
the domestic market, and about growing exports, Hurriyet said.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
